'''2027年亞足聯亞洲盃'''為第19屆的[[亞足聯亞洲盃|亞足聯亞洲盃]]，本屆賽事決賽圈參賽隊伍會有24隊。

==主辦權==
亞足聯證實，以下成員國在截止日期前表示有興趣主辦2027年亞足聯亞洲盃<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-asian-cup/news/five-member-associations-express-interest-to-host-2027-afc-asian-cup|title=Five Member Associations express interest to host 2027 AFC Asian Cup|publisher=AFC|date=1 July 2020|accessdate=2020-08-15|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208094230/https://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-asian-cup/news/five-member-associations-express-interest-to-host-2027-afc-asian-cup|dead-url=no}}</ref>。原定於2021年亞足聯特別大會上宣布東道主，但由于[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]仍在持续，本次大会将推迟到2022年。<ref>{{Cite web|title=COVID-19 effect: Selection for 2027 AFC Asian Cup host postponed to 2022|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/sport/football/2021/jul/21/covid-19-effect-selection-for2027-afc-asian-cup-host-postponed-to-2022-2333408.html|access-date=2021-08-12|work=The New Indian Express|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102092339/https://www.newindianexpress.com/sport/football/2021/jul/21/covid-19-effect-selection-for2027-afc-asian-cup-host-postponed-to-2022-2333408.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*{{flagicon|India}} [[全印足球協會|印度]] –2019年6月5日，[[全印足球協會|全印足球協會]]主席{{link-en|普拉富·帕特爾|Praful Patel}}表達印度有興趣參加2027年亞足聯亞洲盃的申辦<ref>{{Cite web| url=http://www.insideworldfootball.com/2019/06/05/patel-says-india-ambition-stage-2027-asian-cup/| title=Patel says India has ambition to stage 2027 Asian Cup| date=5 June 2019| accessdate=2020-08-15| archive-date=2019-11-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191104004516/http://www.insideworldfootball.com/2019/06/05/patel-says-india-ambition-stage-2027-asian-cup/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。全國聯合會高級官員證實，印度已於2020年4月5日提交了申辦2027年亞足聯亞洲盃的申辦文件<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/football/story/india-officially-submits-bid-to-host-2027-afc-asian-cup-football-tournament-1663568-2020-04-05 | title=We have submitted our expression of interest: AIFF on India's bid to host AFC Asian Cup 2027 | accessdate=2020-08-15 | archive-date=2020-04-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406215303/https://www.indiatoday.in/sports/football/story/india-officially-submits-bid-to-host-2027-afc-asian-cup-football-tournament-1663568-2020-04-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.amarujala.com/sports/football/india-submit-expression-of-interest-to-host-afc-asian-cup-2027 | title=Afc एशियाई कप की मेजबानी के लिए भारत ने पेश किया आधिकारिक दावा | accessdate=2020-08-15 | archive-date=2020-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419113035/https://www.amarujala.com/sports/football/india-submit-expression-of-interest-to-host-afc-asian-cup-2027 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/india-officially-submits-bid-to-host-afc-asian-cup-in-2027/articleshow/74993426.cms | title=India officially submits bid to host AFC Asian Cup in 2027 - Times of India | accessdate=2020-08-15 | archive-date=2020-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718061116/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/top-stories/india-officially-submits-bid-to-host-afc-asian-cup-in-2027/articleshow/74993426.cms | dead-url=no }}</ref>。如果中選，將是亞足聯亞洲盃首度在印度舉辦。
*{{flagicon|Iran}} [[伊朗足球協會|伊朗]] – 2020年4月29日，伊朗宣布有興趣主辦本項賽事，伊朗分別於[[1968年亞足聯亞洲盃|1968年]]和[[1976年亞足聯亞洲盃|1976年]]主辦了本賽事。如果中選，將是伊朗第三次主辦<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.sportbusiness.com/news/iran-submits-bid-to-host-2027-afc-asian-cup/|title = Iran submits bid to host 2027 AFC Asian Cup|date = 29 April 2020|accessdate = 2020-08-15|archive-date = 2020-07-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200718061232/https://www.sportbusiness.com/news/iran-submits-bid-to-host-2027-afc-asian-cup/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

*{{flagicon|Qatar}} [[卡塔尔足球協會|卡塔尔]] – On April 28, 2020, Qatar announced its interests to host the Asian Cup. It will be the third time if Qatar wins the bid.<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1093668/qatar-2027-asian-cup-saudi-arabia | title=Qatar preparing 2027 AFC Asian Cup bid against Saudi Arabia | accessdate=2020-08-15 | archive-date=2020-06-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200608163538/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1093668/qatar-2027-asian-cup-saudi-arabia | dead-url=no }}</ref> Qatar hosted the Asian Cup twice in [[1988_AFC_Asian_Cup|1988]] and [[2011_AFC_Asian_Cup|2011]].

*{{flagicon|Saudi Arabia}} [[沙特足球協會|沙特]] – Saudi Arabia has announced attention to host the competition on February 6, 2020. If this is successful, this will be the first time the Asian Cup to be hosted in Saudi Arabia.<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1090189/saudi-arabia-2027-asian-cup-bid | title=Saudi Arabia bids for 2027 AFC Asian Cup | accessdate=2020-08-15 | archive-date=2020-07-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718063137/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1090189/saudi-arabia-2027-asian-cup-bid | dead-url=no }}</ref>

